##! Please refer to the documentation at
##! https://coreruleset.org/docs/development/regex_assembly/.

##! Detect Unix shell history invocation / bash negation pattern (!-f, !-d, etc.)
##! Require boundary prefix to avoid FP on product codes containing !-digits

##!+ i

##! Require non-word boundary prefix (start of value or after non-word char)
##! This prevents false positives on strings like "abc!-1" or SKU codes
(?:^|\W)!-\d
